  "instructions": [
    "Heat a tablespoon of oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and sauté until they start to pop, about 30 seconds.",
    "Add garlic and onion, sauté for 2-3 minutes or until onions are translucent.",
    "Add cashews and stir fry for another minute.",
    "Stir in turmeric powder and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the broccoli florets and bell peppers to the pan. Stir-fry everything together for about 5 minutes, making sure the vegetables are tender but not mushy.",
    "Garnish with chopped coriander leaves just before serving."
